scenes.description: Biboo, La+ Darknesss, and Amane Kanata performing 'Make It Out Alive' on a fiery stage.
MC section. The three celebrate defeating the enemies. Kanata gives Biboo a coin. Biboo leaves abruptly.
Biboo lands in a retro arcade area (First Stage/Safe Zone). She talks to the audience and decides to take a nap.
Biboo singing 'Flow' while lying on the arcade floor.
